# .lycheeignore: URL exclusions for the Logos docs link check.
# Regex, one per line. URLs only; use --exclude-path for file paths.

# eprint.iacr.org — Cloudflare managed challenge (cf-mitigated: challenge).
# Requires JS execution to obtain clearance; no lychee config can pass it.
# Links confirmed reachable in browser.
^https://eprint\.iacr\.org

# app.notion.com — client-rendered SPA. Lychee only ever receives a JS shell,
# Mantle spec page confirmed publicly reachable in incognito.
^https://app\.notion\.com

# Logos Docs project board. Only accessible to Logos CCs.
^https://github.com/orgs/logos-co/projects/9

# Raspberrypi website. Link confirmed reachable in browser.
^https://www\.raspberrypi\.com/software/

# LEZ public testnet
^https://testnet\.lez\.logos.co/